data.details:
Have you ever wondered about our place in the universe? Come to the Astronomy Carousel weekend, and discover the moon, the sun and the stars in a way you've never seen before. We'll enjoy stargazing, investigate the color spectrum of the stars, talk about plants, lunar phases of the moon and more.

Camp with your Girl Scout troop at this fun-filled weekend! Program is provided. Troops bring their girls for the camping experience and are asked to bring their own meals and camping supplies. Carousel is a perfect introduction to camping for your troop's first time in the woods and a great event to attend more than once a year, as each Carousel Weekend is unique.

Registration ends Oct. 26, 2014 at 11:59 p.m.
